properties.Name: CommunicationDevice
properties.Description: An electronic device that can be attached to a network by wireless, telephone network or other means for the purpose of transmitting information.

Columns.Name: DeviceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Device.

Columns.Name: SerialNumber
Columns.Description: The serial number of the device.

Columns.Name: MacAddress
Columns.Description: A MAC address is a hardware identification number that uniquely identifies a device on a network.

Columns.Name: Imei
Columns.Description: The international mobile equipment identity (IMEI) is a unique identity for the mobile equipment and the International Mobile Subscriber Identity (IMSI) is a unique identity for the UICC and the USIM.

Columns.Name: ProcessorClockSpeedGhz
Columns.Description: The processor clock speed in GHz.

Columns.Name: MaximumMemoryGb
Columns.Description: The user equipment maximum memory in GB.

Columns.Name: OperatingSystemId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an operating system.

Columns.Name: OperatingSystemVersion
Columns.Description: The version number of the operating system.

Columns.Name: SoftwareProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a software product.

Columns.Name: SoftwareProductVersionNumber
Columns.Description: The version number of the software product.

Columns.Name: ComputingDeviceTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Computing Device Type.
